# myOperator Design System — Color Tokens

**CRITICAL: NEVER use hardcoded hex colors.** Always use CSS variables:

```css
/* Primary UI */
--semantic-primary: #343E55          /* Primary actions, headers */
--semantic-primary-hover: #2F384D
--semantic-primary-surface: #EBECEE  /* Light bg for primary elements */

/* Brand Accent — interactive elements ONLY */
--semantic-brand: #2BBCCA            /* Focus rings, active states, links */
--semantic-brand-hover: #1F858F
--semantic-brand-surface: #EAF8FA

/* Backgrounds */
--semantic-bg-primary: #FFFFFF       /* Page/card background */
--semantic-bg-ui: #F5F5F5            /* Subtle surface bg */
--semantic-bg-hover: #D5D7DA

/* Text */
--semantic-text-primary: #181D27
--semantic-text-secondary: #343E55
--semantic-text-muted: #717680
--semantic-text-placeholder: #A2A6B1
--semantic-text-link: #4275D6
--semantic-text-inverted: #FFFFFF

/* Borders */
--semantic-border-layout: #E9EAEB
--semantic-border-input: #E9EAEB
--semantic-border-input-focus: #2BBCCA

/* States */
--semantic-error-primary: #F04438;   --semantic-error-surface: #FEF3F2
--semantic-success-primary: #17B26A; --semantic-success-surface: #ECFDF3
--semantic-warning-primary: #F79009; --semantic-warning-surface: #FFFAEB
--semantic-info-primary: #4275D6;    --semantic-info-surface: #ECF1FB

/* Disabled */
--semantic-disabled-primary: #A2A6B1
--semantic-disabled-secondary: #EBECEE
--semantic-disabled-text: #717680
--semantic-disabled-border: #D5D7DA
```

**Figma hex → token mapping:**
| Hex | Token |
|-----|-------|
| `#343E55` | `--semantic-primary` |
| `#F5F5F5` | `--semantic-bg-ui` |
| `#717680` | `--semantic-text-muted` |
| `#F04438` | `--semantic-error-primary` |
| `#17B26A` | `--semantic-success-primary` |
| `#E9EAEB` | `--semantic-border-layout` |

**Do NOT use turquoise (#2BBCCA) for:** charts, decorative elements, large backgrounds. Use `--semantic-primary` for data visualization.
